(37065, @GROUP_ID+1, 0, 'You will come no further, Forsaken scum!  By the war banner of the ancient Greymane clan, I expel you from our ancestral lands!', 14, 0, 100, 15, 0, 19605, 0, 'Prince Liam Greymane to Player'),
