(38507, @GROUP_ID+4, 0, 'Quick!  Hide in the water!', 12, 0, 100, 15, 0, 19606, 0, 'Tobias Mistmantle to Player'),
(38530, @GROUP_ID+0, 0, 'You can assure Garrosh that this is a minor setback.  Our victory in Gilneas will be absolute.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 19606, 0, 'Lady Sylvanas Windrunner to Player'),
(38530, @GROUP_ID+1, 0, 'You\'d do well to watch your tone, General.  Neither you nor Garrosh have anything to worry about.  We\'ve ceased all production of the Plague, as he ordered.  We\'d never deploy it without his permission.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 19606, 0, 'Lady Sylvanas Windrunner to Player'),
(38530, @GROUP_ID+2, 0, 'Go with honor, General.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 19606, 0, 'Lady Sylvanas Windrunner to Player'),
(38530, @GROUP_ID+3, 0, 'What kind of question is that?  Of course we\'re deploying the Plague as planned!  Let the Gilneans enjoy their small victory.  Not even their bones will remain by tomorrow.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 19606, 0, 'Lady Sylvanas Windrunner to Player'),
(38533, @GROUP_ID+0, 0, 'It appears you\'re losing control of Gilneas, Sylvanas.  Garrosh fears he\'s going to have to carry out this invasion himself.', 12, 0, 100, 66, 0, 19606, 0, 'General Warhowl to Player'),
(38533, @GROUP_ID+1, 0, 'You sound very confident, your Majesty.  I seriously hope you do not plan to use the Plague.  Garrosh has explicitly forbidden it.', 12, 0, 100, 66, 0, 19606, 0, 'General Warhowl to Player'),
(38533, @GROUP_ID+2, 0, 'I will deliver my report to our leader, then.  By your leave, my lady.', 12, 0, 100, 66, 0, 19606, 0, 'General Warhowl to Player'),
(38537, @GROUP_ID+0, 0, 'My Lady!  Should I order my men to stop the deployment of the Plague?  Or are we to continue as planned?', 12, 0, 100, 66, 0, 19606, 0, 'High Executor Crenshaw to Player'),
(38537, @GROUP_ID+1, 0, 'As you wish!', 12, 0, 100, 66, 0, 19606, 0, 'High Executor Crenshaw to Player'),
(38553, @GROUP_ID+0, 0, 'It\'s time to join the fray, $n!  With you on our side the scales will surely tip in our favor!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19606, 0, 'Krennan Aranas to Player'),
(38617, @GROUP_ID+0, 0, 'Make sure everything is ready.  The orcs\' emissary is ready to meet Sylvanas inside the cathedral.', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 19606, 0, 'Forsaken General to Player'),
(38766, @GROUP_ID+0, 0, 'Crowley!  You and your elven allies are hereby ordered to serve along the king\'s army.  Cursed or not, you are still bound by Gilnean law!', 12, 0, 100, 25, 0, 16419, 0, 'Lord Godfrey to Player'),
(38767, @GROUP_ID+0, 0, 'It is decided, then.  We will unite all Gilneans and drive the Forsaken from our lands.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16419, 0, 'King Genn Greymane to Player'),
(38768, @GROUP_ID+0, 0, 'Father!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19605, 0, 'Lorna Crowley to Player'),
(38781, @GROUP_ID+0, 0, 'You did it! We\'re saved!', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 16419, 0, 'Gilnean Survivor to Player'),
(43566, @GROUP_ID+0, 0, 'Attack!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16419, 0, 'Lorna Crowley'),
(43566, @GROUP_ID+1, 0, 'Secure the rafters!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16419, 0, 'Lorna Crowley'),
(43566, @GROUP_ID+2, 0, 'I want two sharpshooters to stay behind and cover the deck.  Everyone else, use the ropes to rappel down.  Let\'s give them hell!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 16419, 0, 'Lorna Crowley'),
